data.text:
In another video from the Ambani event, Abhishek Bachchan was spotted with his wife Aishwarya Rai and daughter Aaradhya. This particular glimpse from the event has made many happy - WATCH

Following customary rituals, Anant Ambani and Radhika Merchant tied the knot on July 12 in front of a large number of celebrities. The Bachchans walked the red carpet at the Jio World Convention Center in Mumbai, much like a ton of other B-town celebrities. While Amitabh Bachchan arrived with his wife Jaya, son Abhishek, daughter Shweta, granddaughter Navya Naveli Nanda, and son-in-law Nikhil Nanda. Aishwarya Rai, on the other hand, arrived with her daughter Aaradhya, sparking separation rumours further. However, as soon as the ‘Ae Dil Hai Mushkil‘ star arrived at the function, Junior Bachchan was seen seated next to her.

Aishwarya And Abhishek Slam Divorce Rumours?

Aishwarya Rai Bachchan’s fans eagerly anticipated to see her glimpses at the Anant and Radhika’s wedding. The actor’s supporter slammed the Bachchan family for leaving her and Aaradhya out of the family. Another video from inside the Ambani event of Aishwarya and Abhishek sitting next to one other has amazed netizens. The mother-daughter duo were seen in the video having a private discussion that ended with laughter.

Aishwarya And Abhishek Enjoy Ambani Event Together – WATCH

Several prominent people from many sectors, including worldwide celebrities, witnessed the marriage of the youngest son of Reliance Industries Chairman Mukesh Ambani and the daughter of businessman Viren Merchant on July 12th. The Jio World Convention Centre in Mumbai hosted Radhika and Anant Ambani’s wedding festivities.
